{"tid":2007751,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"‎‎[瘋狂重畫] 一拳超人 重製的重製版 第145~ 話(新) 集中討論Post","createTime":"2020-05-08T13:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T18:32:48.000Z","uid":130563,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"5b03d72db22d4b49e449b85fa2291620161cc5ed","tid":2007751,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"事緣：<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6KDR1A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6KDR1A.jpg&h=0da50369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在在大幅重畫很久以後才會發售的22卷的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NH5vH8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNH5vH8n.jpg&h=7fea1adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情展開有變化，等原稿畫完了以後，網絡版也會逐一替換。<br />\n到時會通知，請耐心等待<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n175應該仲有排等？<br />\n22卷的內容（由第140話開始）主要係童帝vs鳳凰男<br />\n之前村田仲話過連埼玉VS大蛇嗰段都會改埋，<br />\n所以睇嚟今次唔係小修小改，而係會大改！<br />\n劇情展開有變化，唔知呢個變化有幾大嘅呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXhY8hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXhY8hp.jpg&h=132b3837&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qiPD8hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqiPD8hq.jpg&h=0d377642&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjQeXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjQeXq.jpg&h=e1253dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是為了出單行本重畫的部分。這之後的劇情還沒有調整好，到時會繼續重畫。<br />\n居合鋼的作戰計劃究竟會帶來怎麼樣的影響呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第145話(新)  小心金鋼棒！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第145話(原)：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最先被重畫係第145話，跟住落嚟個蝴蝶效應唔知仲會重畫幾多集，<br />\n希望重畫完眼子仲健在啦..."},{"pid":"d67528cb7a0aec3cb5fd128bdfcbdadd443b7620","tid":2007751,"uid":74901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"完全唔同晒，睇怕有排畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7300384d234d5a332895235a3b1d5a38a1a5e1","tid":2007751,"uid":207012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"為左駁返去one版最新既假面，要重畫洗白佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f975182ec14c1912987e8d6a35507d50fd9057d","tid":2007751,"uid":246838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"依家出到175，由145開始畫，咁重畫到出年都未畫到怪人餓狼LA"},{"pid":"d3ceecd99744bf7dcf44be3bff4c9445a3c79a2c","tid":2007751,"uid":127007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"唔知幾耐先追得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a56d11f9e182d35889c42ee32dc6a8529571b7","tid":2007751,"uid":128089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"咁大整蠱 明明仲等緊佢出175, 竟然又重畫....<br />\n仲要由140開始!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66538f0a8c20548a304afc51c25891d05df2d532","tid":2007751,"uid":52876,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"加果幾隻傭兵蛋散都唔知有咩用<br />\n死完又要改返返生, 而家仲要畫埋護送佢地返地面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed03c3d1ada37154a9d3e1452675569ed68a952d","tid":2007751,"uid":147137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"成個劇情改寫左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係咪打算玩平衡宇宙呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ea161182d120deb2c377f6b619d468311072ad","tid":2007751,"uid":94819,"like":1,"dislike"